From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: tsf-sync contributors <tsf-sync@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Tue, 1 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] wifi: ath10k: add KUnit tests for PTP hardware clock

Table-driven KUnit tests for the ath10k PTP hardware clock.

Test suites:

  ath10k_ptp_direction:
    - inc_tsf/dec_tsf direction selection (11 parameterized cases)
    - zero and sub-us delta early return
    - u32 boundary and overflow truncation

  ath10k_ptp_event:
    - TSF event stores value and signals completion
    - overwrite semantics
    - no-vdev guard (ptp_vdev_id < 0)

  ath10k_ptp_contract:
    - adjfine returns 0 for any input (fixed crystal)

Total: 16 tests.

Signed-off-by: tsf-sync contributors <tsf-sync@users.noreply.github.com>
---
 3 files changed, 280 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

